## SCHEMA REFERENCE (keep this handy)

```sql
-- Table: MSBK_BUS_DTL
SELECT
  MSBK_BUS_DTL_ID,     -- PK
  BUS_DATE,            -- Business date
  MSBK_ID,             -- Master book ID
  REC_ID,              -- Reconciliation ID
  REC_SUBCATEGORY_ID,  -- Sub-category ID
  STATUS,              -- COMPLETE | PROCESSING | PENDING | FAILED
  EXPN,                -- Rec type description
  EXPNCOUNT,           -- Exception count (breaks)
  START_TIME,          -- Processing start
  END_TIME,            -- Processing end (null = still running)
  SERVICE_NAME,        -- Processing service name
  ISHOLIDAY,           -- Y/N
  REGN_ID,             -- APAC | EMEA | AMER
  IN_MOTIF,            -- Y/N — exists in MOTIF system
  BUSINESSAREANAME,    -- Business area
  HIERARCHYLEVEL,      -- Hierarchy level name
  HIERARCHYLEVEL7,     -- Sub-hierarchy level 7
  LASTUPDATE,          -- Row last updated timestamp
  LASTUPDATEDBY        -- Who/what last updated row
FROM MSBK_BUS_DTL
WHERE BUS_DATE = :busDate
ORDER BY START_TIME DESC;
```